============================================
Name: sample-lambda
Description:
  The sample-lambda function returns a mock
  object for use when setting up API Gateway
  methods.
============================================

=================
Local Dev
=================

-----
Install lambda-local
-----
npm install -g lambda-local@0.0.9

-----
Execute lambda via command line
-----
lambda-local  -l sample-lambda.js -e event.json


-----
Execute Tests
-----
npm test

